software-license-agreement.title: Software License Agreement
software-license-agreement.description: License your software to users while protecting your intellectual property rights. Sets usage terms and restrictions.

app-development-agreement.title: App Development Agreement
app-development-agreement.description: Hire developers to create your mobile app. Covers timeline, features, ownership, and what happens if problems arise.

web-development-agreement.title: Web Development Agreement
web-development-agreement.description: Hire web developers to build your website. Protects both parties with clear scope, deadlines, and payment terms.

website-development-agreement.title: Website Development Agreement
website-development-agreement.description: Create professional websites with clear developer agreements. Covers design, functionality, hosting, and maintenance.

cloud-services-agreement.title: Cloud Services Agreement
cloud-services-agreement.description: Use cloud computing services safely for your business. Protects your data and ensures reliable service levels.

data-processing-agreement.title: Data Processing Agreement
data-processing-agreement.description: Ensure customer data is handled properly when using third-party services. Required for GDPR and privacy compliance.

cybersecurity-agreement.title: Cybersecurity Agreement
cybersecurity-agreement.description: Hire cybersecurity experts to protect your business from hackers and data breaches. Essential for digital safety.

ecommerce-terms-of-service.title: Ecommerce Terms Of Service
ecommerce-terms-of-service.description: Set rules for customers using your online store. Protects your business and creates clear expectations for buyers.

digital-asset-agreement.title: Digital Asset Agreement
digital-asset-agreement.description: Buy, sell, or license digital content like images, videos, or software. Protects ownership and usage rights.

cryptocurrency-agreement.title: Cryptocurrency Agreement
cryptocurrency-agreement.description: Handle cryptocurrency transactions safely with legal protections. Covers trading, mining, or investment arrangements.

gaming-agreement.title: Gaming Agreement
gaming-agreement.description: Create or license video games with clear terms. Covers development, publishing, revenue sharing, and player rights.

music-license-agreement.title: Music License Agreement
music-license-agreement.description: Use music legally in your projects. Covers licensing fees, usage rights, and restrictions for commercial use.

music-licensing-agreement.title: Music Licensing Agreement
music-licensing-agreement.description: Advanced music licensing for complex projects. Covers multiple songs, territories, and commercial usage rights.

video-release.title: Video Release
video-release.description: Get permission to use someone's image in videos or films. Protects you from privacy lawsuits and usage claims.
